We Can also Add a type of a function like this:

type AddFn = (a:number,b:number) => number;

let add:AddFn;
add =(n1:number, n2:number)=>{
    return n1+n2;
}

===================================================================================================

You can also create function type with Interface

interface AddFn{
    (a:number, b:number):number;
}

The Above code will behave as function type:
let add:AddFn
add=(a:number, b:number) =>{
    return a+b;
}